---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import collage from "../assets/images/Collage.webp";
---

<section class="about">
<Image src={collage} alt="Collage of photos of Saravanan" width={500} class="collage" />
<div class="right">

<h2>Boxing Trainer / Owner of Lethal Kickboxing Academy</h2>
<h3>Saravanan</h3>
<p>Lethal Kickboxing Academy, founded by Saravanan in Perambur, is a combat sports and fitness institution born from a deep passion for martial arts and fitness. With a kickboxing background, Saravanan envisioned a place where diverse individuals, from students to professionals, could realize their unique goals. The Academy offers customized programs, supporting students in their journey, whether it's preparing for a competitive fight, learning self-defense, or achieving peak physical fitness. Beyond martial arts, it has evolved into a community hub, fostering encouragement, empowerment, and a sense of belonging. Witnessing transformations in physical fitness, character, confidence, and discipline, the academy stands as a testament to Saravanan's passion. It's not just about martial arts; it's about guiding individuals to become their best selves.</p>
</div>

</section>

<style>
  .about {
    display: flex;
    padding: 5% 13%;
    gap: 2rem;
    background-color: #111111;
}

.about .right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
}

h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #F1C644;
}

h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #F1C644;
}
p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
}

@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .about {
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 5% 5%;
    }
    .about .right {
        gap: 1rem;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #F1C644;
    }
    h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #F1C644;
    }
    p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
        text-align: left;
    }
  .collage {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }
}
</style>